Package: response
Title: Mean and Confidence Intervals of a Response Variable by Group
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("James", "Edwards", , "jamese1326@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Gives mean and confidence intervals of a response variable by groups of an 
    input variable. The response can be numeric with confidence intervals calculated 
    using Gaussian assumptions, or if the response has two classes then a binomial c
    confidence interval can be used.
